{{American cuisine}}
{{Cuisine of China}}
{{use American English|date=February 2019}}

'''American Chinese cuisine''' is a style of [[Chinese cuisine]] developed by [[Chinese Americans]]. The dishes served in many North American [[Chinese restaurant]]s are adapted to American tastes and often differ significantly from those found in China.

